name: DawgNation
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: UGA fans get their Georgia Bulldogs news from DawgNation.com. And now you can get those DawgNation headlines delivered daily on Alexa. DawgNation Daily host, Brandon Adams provides the daily scoop from the DawgNation reporters in Athens and the latest recruiting news from Jeff Sentell. Add DawgNation to your daily flash briefing to stay up to date on UGA athletics.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
